-- China May Start Trial Property Tax Before March, Securities Journal Says
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-24T23:18:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-24/china-may-start-trial-property-tax-before-march-securities-journal-says.html
China may start levying a property
tax on a trial basis before March next year, the China
Securities Journal reported today, citing Nie Meisheng,
president of the China Real Estate Chamber of Commerce.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
